{{NASTRO comment}}
{{DEFAULTSORT:Anshan}} [[Category:Background asteroids|003136]] [[Category:Discoveries by the Purple Mountain Observatory|003136]] [[Category:Minor planets named for places]] [[Category:Named minor planets]] [[Category:Astronomical objects discovered in 1981|19811118]]

'''Bayport''' is the city used as the setting in the [[Hardy Boys]] novels. In the books it is located on [[Barmet Bay]], a horseshoe-shaped inlet three miles from the [[Atlantic Ocean]] in the [[Northeastern United States]].  It is the residence of [[Fenton Hardy (The Hardy Boys)|The Hardy family]] and [[Chet Morton|The Morton Family]].

Most books are intentionally vague about what [[U.S. state|state]] Bayport is in, though ''[[The Castle Conundrum]]'' definitively places it in [[New York (state)|New York]], which does have a [[Bayport, New York|Bayport]] on [[Long Island]].

