'''C17''' is an untarred road in the eastern part of [[ǁKaras Region]] in [[Namibia]]. It starts at the [[C15 road (Namibia)|C15]] and [[Auob River]], a couple of kilometers inside of [[Hardap Region]] before ending {{Convert|369|km}} later in [[Keetmanshoop]].

