This is a '''list of diplomatic missions of Benin'''. Owing to its small size, the [[Benin|Republic of Benin]] maintains a very modest diplomatic network abroad. Its paramount relationship is with [[France]], the former colonial power.

Honorary consulates are excluded from this list.

